Package: sovpal
Title: Soviet and Industrial Color Palettes
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Kinan", "El Husseini", email = "kinelhu@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Color palettes derived from Soviet military paint standards, GOST
    industrial pipeline color codes, safety signage, and avant-garde artworks.
    Each palette has a thematic domain (industrial, military, artistic, or
    composite) and a functional type (qualitative, sequential, or diverging).
    Artistic palettes are color-sampled from specific Constructivist and
    Suprematist works. Includes ggplot2 scale functions, computed
    white-background contrast reporting, and is structured for ingestion into
    'paletteer'.
